    "Refractive index <katex>$\\mu = \\frac{\\sin(\\frac{A+\\delta_m}{2})}{\\sin(A/2)} = \\frac{\\sin(60)}{\\sin(30)} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}/2}{1/2} = \\sqrt{3}$</katex>.",
